title: Add New Column to a Table in Mysql
tags: @zettel _method mysql
roam-id: 6c65b115-f156-4e50-b68a-91a551336031
type: text/markdown

``` sql
ALTER TABLE table_name ADD COLUMN column_name data_type;
```

real example:

``` sql
ALTER TABLE bulk_coin_charging ADD COLUMN coin_completion_enabled bit(1);
```
